Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.05,0:05:01.84,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:301051,301843}No.{NOTE:いいえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.84,0:05:04.51,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:301843,304513}Listen. I'm sure this is it.{NOTE:いい？あの人達に決まっている。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.51,0:05:07.51,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:304513,307516}They're jealous of our skill and popularity.{NOTE:私達の実力と人気を妬んでいるのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.51,0:05:09.97,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:307516,309976}And that's why they're trying to get rid of us by all means.{NOTE:だから追い出すためにこんな酷いことを。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.97,0:05:11.26,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:309976,311269}I can't take it anymore.{NOTE:私もう我慢できない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.94,0:05:17.48,Default,Kanda,0,0,0,,{TIME:315941,317484}What's with the racket?{NOTE:何よいきなり。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.48,0:05:19.65,Default,Kanda,0,0,0,,{TIME:317484,319653}Would it kill you to enter in a more civilized way?{NOTE:もっと静かに入ってきたらどうよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.65,0:05:20.57,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:319653,320570}Captain.{NOTE:キャプテン。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.57,0:05:23.11,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:320570,323114}Kozue was blinded with lime!{NOTE:こずえは石灰で目が見えなくなったのよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.11,0:05:23.74,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:323114,323740}Huh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.44,0:05:29.07,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:324449,329079}How far are you willing to go to drive us out?{NOTE:あなた達いくら私達を追い出したいからって、何て汚い手を使うの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.07,0:05:32.04,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:329079,332040}You were the ones who put lime on Kozue's towel!{NOTE:こずえのタオルに石灰をつけておいたのはあなた達でしょう！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.04,0:05:32.95,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:332040,332958}Hayakawa-san.{NOTE:早川さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.95,0:05:34.50,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:332958,334501}Do you understand what you're saying?{NOTE:それどう言うことなの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.50,0:05:36.12,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:334501,336127}I have no idea about any lime.{NOTE:石灰なんて知らないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.12,0:05:39.13,Default,Nakahara,0,0,0,,{TIME:336127,339130}Don't throw ridiculous accusations at us.{NOTE:あなた、私達に言いがかりをつけるきね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.13,0:05:40.46,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:339130,340465}Don't screw with me!{NOTE:XXXないで！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.46,0:05:44.38,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:340465,344386}Do you think I'm going to keep my mouth shut\Nafter what you've done to my friend?!{NOTE:親友をこんな目に会ったれて、それで、それで黙ってる私だ思ってるの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.38,0:05:47.05,Default,Kanda,0,0,0,,{TIME:344386,347055}Oh, this just got interesting.{NOTE:へぇ？いいたいこと言ってくれるじゃん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.05,0:05:48.97,Default,Kanda,0,0,0,,{TIME:347055,348974}But we won't forgive you talking smack about us either.{NOTE:そこまで言われた許せないぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.97,0:05:51.01,Default,Kanda,0,0,0,,{TIME:348974,351017}Do you even have any proof that we did it?{NOTE:どこにそんな証拠あるんだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.01,0:05:51.93,Default,Suga,0,0,0,,{TIME:351017,351935}Right.{NOTE:そうよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.93,0:05:54.43,Default,Suga,0,0,0,,{TIME:351935,354437}How about you show us evidence right here, right now?{NOTE:証拠があるのは今直ぐ出してみたらいいんじゃないの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.43,0:05:55.10,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:354437,355105}Fine.{NOTE:いいわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.10,0:05:56.31,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:355105,356314}I'll show it now.{NOTE:今見せてあげます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.56,0:06:01.23,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:359568,361236}The towel's gone!{NOTE:ない！タオルが！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.23,0:06:03.11,Default,Nakahara,0,0,0,,{TIME:361236,363113}Where's your evidence?{NOTE:どうしたのよ？証拠は。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.65,0:06:07.99,Default,Nakahara,0,0,0,,{TIME:365657,367993}Maybe there wasn't one from the beginning.{NOTE:証拠何て初めからあるもんですか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.99,0:06:08.95,Default,Suga,0,0,0,,{TIME:367993,368952}Yeah.{NOTE:そうよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.95,0:06:11.20,Default,Suga,0,0,0,,{TIME:368952,371204}You talk so big, but you've got nothing to back it up.{NOTE:証拠もないのに大きいな口を叩かないでよね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.20,0:06:13.58,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:371204,373582}– Yeah.\N– What's with her?{NOTE:—そうよね。\\N—何よ。\\N—一体何だって。\\N—ははは。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.58,0:06:16.41,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:373582,376418}{\fad(0,500)}Volleyball club's room{NOTE:バレー部々室}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.50,0:06:18.21,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:376501,378211}I'm sorry, Hayakawa-san.{NOTE:早川さん、ごめんなさいね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.54,0:06:24.71,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:382549,384718}Kozue. Can you recognize my face?{NOTE:こずえ。ママの顔が見える？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.71,0:06:25.59,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:384718,385594}You can see it, right?{NOTE:見えるのね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.59,0:06:28.22,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:386595,388221}Mama. What happened?{NOTE:ママ。どうしたの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.47,0:06:31.09,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:389472,391099}It's over. Everything's okay now.{NOTE:よかったね。もう大丈夫よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.76,0:06:33.31,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:391766,393310}Naka. Midori, you too?{NOTE:ナカ、それにみどりも。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.06,0:06:35.02,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:394060,395020}Kozue.{NOTE:こずえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.02,0:06:39.27,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:395020,399274}You lost your sight and collapsed in the middle of the game.{NOTE:あなたはね、試合の途中で目が見えなくなって倒れてしまったのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.27,0:06:41.19,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:399274,401192}Ah, now I remember.{NOTE:あ、そうだったわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.19,0:06:42.44,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:401192,402444}Midori, what about the game?{NOTE:それで、みどり、試合は？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.44,0:06:43.57,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:402444,403570}How did it end?{NOTE:試合はどうなったの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.32,0:06:47.03,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:404321,407032}It was a complete defeat for Fujimi High School.{NOTE:完敗だったわ。富士見高校の。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.49,0:06:48.45,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:407490,408450}Huh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.45,0:06:50.41,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:408450,410410}Then we're gonna have to…{NOTE:じゃ、私達バレー部を…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.41,0:06:51.32,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:410410,411328}Yeah.{NOTE:そうなの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.32,0:06:54.03,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:411328,414039}We've already dropped out of the club.{NOTE:私達もう退部させられてしまったの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.03,0:06:54.99,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:414039,414998}Huh?!{NOTE:え？！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.45,0:07:00.58,Alternative,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:417459,420587}If you don't show your worth during that match… if you don't…!{NOTE:実力は伴わないと分かったら…その時は！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.58,0:07:01.79,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:420587,421796}I understand.{NOTE:分かっています。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.71,0:07:06.67,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:425717,426676}Kozue.{NOTE:こずえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.67,0:07:08.63,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:426676,428637}I have no proof, but bear with me.{NOTE:証拠もないからどうしようもないけど…}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.63,0:07:11.59,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:428637,431598}When the first set was over,\Nyou wiped your face with a towel, didn't you?{NOTE:ワンセットの終わった時、こずえがタオルで顔を拭いたでしょ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.59,0:07:12.68,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:431598,432682}Do you remember?{NOTE:覚えてる？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.68,0:07:15.18,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:432682,435185}Someone put lime on that towel.{NOTE:あのタオルに石灰をつけっといた人がいるのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.18,0:07:15.68,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:435185,435685}Huh!?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.68,0:07:17.43,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:435685,437437}Who could have done that!?{NOTE:そんな酷いこと？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.43,0:07:20.31,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:437437,440315}I hope they don't think\NI'll just let them get away with this!{NOTE:私このまま黙って引き下がって何かいないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.02,0:07:22.02,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:441024,442025}Kozue.{NOTE:こずえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.02,0:07:24.40,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:442025,444402}Midori-san has told me the whole story.{NOTE:そのことはみどりさんから聞きました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.40,0:07:29.24,Default,Ayuhara's mom,1,1,0,,{TIME:444402,449240}But you shouldn't do anything rash without any proof,\Notherwise you might harm innocent people.{NOTE:でもはっきりしない家はXXX傷つけるような真似をしてはいけませんよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.24,0:07:30.32,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:449240,450325}But…{NOTE:でも。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.32,0:07:32.03,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:450325,452035}But this is too much!{NOTE:でも、あんまりだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.03,0:07:36.79,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:452035,456790}I bet my future in volleyball on this one game.{NOTE:私、私命とも思ってれバレーをこんな試合一つにかけたのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.79,0:07:39.91,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:456790,459918}To lose it like that…{NOTE:そ、それが…こ、こんな負け方は…}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.91,0:07:41.71,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:459918,461711}I can't stand this!{NOTE:私が我慢できない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.71,0:07:44.04,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:461711,464047}I understand you, Chief.{NOTE:分かるよ、親分。その気持ち。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.04,0:07:45.92,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:464047,465924}Kozue.{NOTE:こずえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.30,0:07:56.30,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:471304,476309}{\1c&H101010&\3c&H101010&\4c&H101010&\t(0,1500,\1c&H9AFBDC&\3c&H202020&\4c&H202020&)}Fujimi High School{NOTE:富士見高校学校}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.10,0:07:57.31,Default,Student,0,0,0,,{TIME:476101,477310}It's A-Ayuhara-san.{NOTE:あ、鮎原さんだ。}
