Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.35,0:08:06.02,Default,Katsuragi,0,0,0,,{TIME:483358,486027}You were driven out of the club like I told you.{NOTE:やっぱりバレー部を追い出されてしまったわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.02,0:08:08.73,Default,Katsuragi,0,0,0,,{TIME:486027,488738}Why don't you play basketball with us instead?{NOTE:どう？私の言うとおりバスケット部に転向しない？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.73,0:08:10.90,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:488738,490907}Thank you.{NOTE:え。有り難うございます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.90,0:08:13.82,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:490907,493827}But right now I feel really tired.{NOTE:でも、私、なんだかすごく疲れちゃったんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.82,0:08:15.87,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:493827,495870}I'm sorry.{NOTE:だから、ごめんなさい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.91,0:08:19.49,Alternative,Katsuragi,0,0,0,,{TIME:496913,499499}Ayuhara-san, a person like you…{NOTE:鮎原さん。あなたと言う人。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.49,0:08:21.83,Alternative,Katsuragi,0,0,0,,{TIME:499499,501835}…no matter what she's put through, will not give up.{NOTE:こんなにまでされても、バレーを捨てることが出来ない。}
