Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.38,0:08:28.50,Default,Student,0,0,0,,{TIME:506381,508508}Have you heard the news about the volleyball club?{NOTE:知ってたよ？バレー部のゴタゴタ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.50,0:08:28.88,Default,Student,0,0,0,,{TIME:508508,508883}Eh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.88,0:08:34.51,Default,Student,1,1,0,,{TIME:508883,514514}Well, they say the one who burned Ayuhara Kozue's eyes with lime was one of Oonuma Miyuki's followers.{NOTE:あのね、鮎原こずえの目をね、石灰で潰したと言うのはどうやら大沼みゆきの一味だそうだぜ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.51,0:08:35.64,Default,Student,0,0,0,,{TIME:514514,515640}You don't say!{NOTE:ま、本当？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.64,0:08:37.05,Default,Student,0,0,0,,{TIME:515640,517058}Hey, hey!{NOTE:え、ちょっと、ちょっと！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.05,0:08:39.85,Default,Student,0,0,0,,{TIME:517058,519853}Oonuma Miyuki burned Ayuhara Kozue's eyes!{NOTE:大沼みゆきさんが鮎原こずえさんの目を潰したそうよ。}
