Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.02,0:08:51.90,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:529029,531906}The thing from yesterday became the hottest topic at school.{NOTE:昨日のことはね、学校中の評判になってるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.90,0:08:52.86,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:531906,532866}Eh?{NOTE:え？}
