Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.49,0:09:04.25,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:541499,544252}Well, it has nothing to do with us either way.{NOTE:どっちにしたって、私達と何の関係もないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.25,0:09:06.29,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:544252,546296}We're better off staying away from it.{NOTE:そんなこと放っとけばいいじゃないの。}
