Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.78,0:09:40.99,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:579788,580997}Yes ma'am.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.99,0:09:42.29,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:580997,582290}Every afternoon…{NOTE:Every afternoon…}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.66,0:09:44.91,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:583666,584918}Ahh.{NOTE:あぁ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.91,0:09:48.63,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:584918,588630}When I can't play volleyball, everything starts to remind me of it.{NOTE:バレーができないと何と何を見てもバレーボールに見えてくるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.63,0:09:49.92,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:588630,589923}This is no good.{NOTE:こんなことじゃいけない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.92,0:09:51.59,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:589923,591591}I need to forget about it soon.{NOTE:速くバレーのこと忘れなきゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.55,0:09:58.13,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:596554,598139}Thanks for waiting, Kozue.{NOTE:こずえ。お待ちどおさま。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.13,0:09:59.72,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:598139,599724}Oh. Going home?{NOTE:あ、帰ろうか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.72,0:10:00.55,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:599724,600558}Yeah.{NOTE:え。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.93,0:10:05.98,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:601935,605980}Doesn't it feel strange going home this early?{NOTE:でも、こんな早時間に家へ帰るなんて、変な気分ね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.98,0:10:09.56,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:605980,609567}I honestly don't know what to do with myself at home.{NOTE:家へ帰ったら、何をしようかな。困っちゃう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.56,0:10:11.06,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:609567,611069}I'm hoping you have some ideas?{NOTE:きっとXXXわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.06,0:10:13.07,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:611069,613071}I start new school term by reading a book.{NOTE:新期って行って本を読むのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.07,0:10:13.86,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:613071,613863}A book.{NOTE:本を。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.86,0:10:14.86,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:613863,614864}And also—{NOTE:えっと、それか—}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.86,0:10:15.57,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:614864,615573}Eh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.57,0:10:19.45,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{TIME:615573,619452}Oh, so Miss Volleyball wants to turn into a book worm?{NOTE:あ、バレーの(XXX・意外一転)して読書をする少女に変わるとはね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.45,0:10:21.24,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:619452,621246}What's with the sarcasm, Mitamura-kun?{NOTE:三田村くん、それ皮肉？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.24,0:10:22.99,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{TIME:621246,622997}It just doesn't feel like you.{NOTE:何、ただ様にならないからさ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.16,0:10:26.75,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:624165,626751}I see you know what suits us\Nbetter than we do, huh?{NOTE:どうせい私達には似合わないでしょうよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.75,0:10:28.21,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{TIME:626751,628211}Yeah, maybe I do know.{NOTE:あ、似合わんな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.21,0:10:30.08,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{TIME:628211,630088}I heard some gossip about you.{NOTE:君達の噂は聞いたけどさ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.08,0:10:33.75,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{TIME:630088,633758}Really, now? Is that seriously all it takes to bring you down?{NOTE:何だ？まさかそれくらいことで挫けるとは思わなかったぜ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.88,0:10:36.55,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{TIME:634884,636553}Where's your usual enthusiasm?{NOTE:一体どうなんだ？本心は。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.59,0:10:38.47,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:637595,638471}Right.{NOTE:え。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.26,0:10:42.10,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:639264,642100}He's right, you know.\NIt's just like Mitamura-kun says.{NOTE:そうなのよ。三田村くんの言う通りだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.10,0:10:46.18,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:642100,646187}No matter how much I try to forget about volleyball, my mind keeps going back to it.{NOTE:いくら忘れようと思っても、どうしてもバレーのことがついて回ってくるのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.18,0:10:47.23,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:646187,647230}I'm the same.{NOTE:私もよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.23,0:10:52.48,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:647230,652485}That's why I don't know what to do anymore. It's like between a rock and a hard place.{NOTE:だからさ、どうしていいのか自分で自分が分かんないのよ。もう悔しくて悲しくてた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.48,0:10:54.57,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{TIME:652485,654571}Do you feel the same, Ayuhara-kun?{NOTE:鮎原くんだって同じだろう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.57,0:10:55.44,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:654571,655446}Yeah.{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.44,0:10:57.78,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{TIME:655446,657782}Well, either way, the current girls volleyball club is no good.{NOTE:とにかく女子バレー部なってない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.78,0:11:00.32,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{TIME:657782,660326}In my opinion, it's clearly its advisor,\NProfessor Shimizu's, fault.{NOTE:これも部長の清水先生がいけないんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.32,0:11:02.37,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{TIME:660326,662370}I wonder if a woman is fit for such position…{NOTE:女の先生には無理なのかな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.37,0:11:04.91,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{TIME:662370,664914}See, she feels like she's just a puppet for show.{NOTE:第一あれじゃ飾り人形にすぎんよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.91,0:11:07.25,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{TIME:664914,667250}Why would she even become an advisor?{NOTE:なんのための部長が分からんぜ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.25,0:11:09.50,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{TIME:667250,669502}Anyway, that's exactly why you've gotta patch things up by yourselves.{NOTE:だからさ、君たちがやらなきゃいけないんだよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.37,0:11:12.00,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{TIME:670378,672005}Keep fighting!{NOTE:さ、ファイト！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.00,0:11:13.67,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{TIME:672005,673673}And cheer up!{NOTE:さ、元気出せよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.67,0:11:14.54,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{TIME:673673,674549}Alright, gotta run.{NOTE:じゃ、又な。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.54,0:11:15.96,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{TIME:674549,675967}I've got soccer practice now.{NOTE:これからサッカーの練習なんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.55,0:11:18.63,Default,Ishikawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:677552,678636}Ayuhara-san!{NOTE:鮎原さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.63,0:11:19.30,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:678636,679304}Ah?{NOTE:あ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.01,0:11:23.09,Default,Ishikawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:680013,683099}Uhm, our captain called for you.\NShe wants you to come to the club room.{NOTE:あの、キャプテンがあなた達呼んでるの。部室に来て欲しいって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.09,0:11:24.35,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:683099,684350}– Eh?\N– Eh?{NOTE:—え？\\N—え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.89,0:11:26.93,Default,Kanda,0,0,0,,{TIME:684893,686936}Don't you think she did it on purpose?{NOTE:徹底的にやるべきをそう思わない？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.93,0:11:27.60,Default,Suga,0,0,0,,{TIME:686936,687604}She's here.{NOTE:来たわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.89,0:11:32.10,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:689898,692108}What did you call us for?{NOTE:私達によって何ですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.10,0:11:34.19,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:692108,694194}I bet you already know, don't you?{NOTE:言われなくたって分かってるでしょう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.11,0:11:36.15,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:695111,696154}No, I don't.{NOTE:分からないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.15,0:11:37.61,Default,Kanda,0,0,0,,{TIME:696154,697614}Wow, playing innocent.{NOTE:よ！涼しい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.61,0:11:40.61,Default,Kanda,0,0,0,,{TIME:697614,700617}You're the ones who spread all those rumors!{NOTE:根も葉もない噂を散蒔いたのはあんたたちでしょうよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.57,0:11:43.66,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:701576,703661}What? I have no idea what you're talking about.{NOTE:え？知らないわ、そんなこと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.66,0:11:44.62,Default,Suga,0,0,0,,{TIME:703661,704621}What a liar.{NOTE:嘘っしゃい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.62,0:11:47.33,Default,Suga,0,0,0,,{TIME:704621,707332}Thanks to the rumors you spread, our club's prestige went downhill.{NOTE:ありもしない噂のおかげでバレー部の名誉めちゃめちゃなのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.33,0:11:48.37,Default,Suga,0,0,0,,{TIME:707332,708374}Why did you do it?{NOTE:どうしてくれるをした？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.37,0:11:50.58,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:708374,710585}Why…? But we didn't do any—{NOTE:どうしてって…私達何も…}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.58,0:11:52.25,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:710585,712253}You're pretty bold, you know that?{NOTE:あなた達っていんけんね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.25,0:11:53.37,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:712253,713379}I guess we've misjudged you.{NOTE:見損なった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.37,0:11:56.38,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:713379,716382}Backstabbing like that\Nis completely unsportsmanlike.{NOTE:陰でこそこそするなんてスポーツマンらしくないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.38,0:11:58.46,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:716382,718468}B-But we didn't do anything!{NOTE:ち、違うわ私達。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.34,0:12:00.97,Default,Nakahara,0,0,0,,{TIME:719344,720970}Stop pretending.{NOTE:弁解なんかしないで。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.97,0:12:02.26,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:720970,722263}We're not pretending.{NOTE:弁解じゃないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.26,0:12:05.14,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:722263,725141}You were the ones who backstabbed us.{NOTE:陰でこそこそしたのはあなた達の方でしょ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.14,0:12:07.06,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:725141,727060}W-What?!{NOTE:な、何ですって？！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.64,0:12:11.64,Default,Kanda,0,0,0,,{TIME:729646,731648}What are you doing to our Captain?!\NKnow your place!{NOTE:キャプテンに何すんだ？！生意気だぞ！}
Comment: 0,0:12:18.65,0:12:18.65,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:738655,738655}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.49,0:12:24.49,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:743493,744494}Captain!?{NOTE:キャプテン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.49,0:12:27.70,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:744494,747705}Captain. These rumors are not unfounded.{NOTE:キャプテン。これは根も葉もない噂じゃありません。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.70,0:12:30.29,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:747705,750291}There can't be so much smoke without a fire.{NOTE:火のないところに煙は立たないと思います。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.87,0:12:32.75,Default,Ishikawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:751876,752752}I agree.{NOTE:そうよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.75,0:12:37.59,Default,Ishikawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:752752,757590}We all found this thing that happened with Ayuhara-san strange, and we discussed it together.{NOTE:ここにいる私達皆も自分の目で見て変だと思ったから話したまでだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.59,0:12:39.67,Default,Ishikawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:757590,759676}Ayuhara-san didn't spread that gossip.{NOTE:噂をしたのは鮎原さん達じゃなく。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.67,0:12:41.30,Default,Ishikawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:759676,761302}It was all of us!{NOTE:私達皆です。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.30,0:12:43.22,Default,Kanda,0,0,0,,{TIME:761302,763221}What… what are you saying?!{NOTE:な、何よ、あんた達！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.22,0:12:45.39,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:763221,765390}– That's right.\N– I talked about it too.{NOTE:—そうよ。\\N—私もXX。\\N—ね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.26,0:12:50.97,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:766266,770979}We didn't have the courage until today\Nand so we did as you pleased…{NOTE:私達今日まで勇気がなくて、あなた方の言うがままになってきたけど…}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.97,0:12:52.43,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:770979,772438}But we can't take it anymore!{NOTE:もう我慢じゃできないわ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.43,0:12:53.27,Default,Ishikawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:772438,773273}Yeah!{NOTE:そうよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.27,0:12:56.31,Default,Ishikawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:773273,776317}I've had enough of your messed up "traditions"\Nand being under your thumb!{NOTE:あなた方にばかりXXX伝統なんてごめんだわ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.31,0:12:56.90,Default,Student,0,0,0,,{TIME:776317,776901}Right!{NOTE:そうよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.90,0:12:58.15,Default,Student,0,0,0,,{TIME:776901,778152}What's with these "traditions"?{NOTE:伝統なんて何よ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.15,0:12:59.32,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:778152,779320}– Exactly!\N– Whoa, whoa!{NOTE:—そうよ！\\N—あんた達！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.32,0:13:00.98,Default,Kanda,0,0,0,,{TIME:779320,780989}Rebelling against your seniors?{NOTE:上級生に逆らうつもりなの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.98,0:13:01.82,Default,Kanda,0,0,0,,{TIME:780989,781823}Talk about a bad attitude!{NOTE:態度悪いぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.82,0:13:03.32,Default,Kanda,0,0,0,,{TIME:781823,783324}Yeah! You're way out of line!{NOTE:そうだ！態度大きいぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.32,0:13:04.07,Default,Suga,0,0,0,,{TIME:783324,784075}Impudent lasses!{NOTE:生意気よ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.07,0:13:05.82,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:784075,785827}I won't forgive a rebellion!{NOTE:—そうだ！\\N—XXX何て許さないわ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.82,0:13:08.41,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:785827,788413}Who's the ringleader?! Step forward!{NOTE:で、XX首謀者なの前に出て！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.91,0:13:10.45,Default,Ishikawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:788913,790456}There isn't one! We're all in this together!{NOTE:誰でもないわ！皆よ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.45,0:13:11.49,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:790456,791499}Yeah!{NOTE:そうよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.49,0:13:12.91,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:791499,792917}Wait.{NOTE:待って。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.91,0:13:14.83,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:792917,794836}Girls, that's no good.{NOTE:皆駄目よ。いけないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.83,0:13:16.83,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:794836,796838}Ayuhara-san, why are you stopping us?{NOTE:鮎原さん、どうして止めるの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.83,0:13:19.79,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:796838,799799}You had it worst.{NOTE:あなた達が一番酷い目に会わされたじゃないの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.79,0:13:20.63,Default,Ishikawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:799799,800633}Exactly…{NOTE:そうよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.63,0:13:23.21,Default,Ishikawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:800633,803219}You've got the most reasons to resist her!{NOTE:あなた達こそ(XX・末席に残る)べきだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.21,0:13:24.17,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:803219,804178}Wait.{NOTE:待って。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.17,0:13:27.34,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:804178,807348}I don't think we're going to solve anything like this.{NOTE:こんなことでは問題の解決にはならないと思うわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.34,0:13:28.26,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:807348,808266}But…{NOTE:だって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.26,0:13:31.47,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:808266,811477}But if we don't do it this way, it won't get to them!{NOTE:だってこうでもしなきゃ、この人達に分かんないのよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.47,0:13:35.35,Default,Ishikawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:811477,815356}We stood up thanks to Ayuhara-san's group's courage!{NOTE:私達鮎原さん達の勇気のおかげで立ち上がったんだわ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.35,0:13:37.35,Default,Ishikawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:815356,817358}I can't hold back anymore!{NOTE:もう！後には引けないわ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.35,0:13:39.27,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:817358,819277}– Yeah!\N– What's so special about you!{NOTE:—そうよ！\\N—XXX}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.69,0:13:42.36,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:820695,822363}Wait! Stop it!{NOTE:待って！止めて！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.36,0:13:43.86,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:822363,823865}If you're not helping, don't stop us!{NOTE:XXXしないで！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.49,0:13:46.65,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:824490,826659}I've been waiting for this!{NOTE:XXX！XXしなきゃ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.74,0:13:51.99,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:829746,831998}Don't stop!{NOTE:XXX！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.99,0:13:54.29,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:831998,834292}Finally, it's payback time!{NOTE:よくも私達XXお返しよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.04,0:13:56.46,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:835043,836461}Payback time…!{NOTE:お返しよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.46,0:14:00.84,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:838463,840840}S-Stop it! Cut it out!{NOTE:や、止めてよ！いけないわ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.80,0:14:07.30,Default,Student,0,0,0,,{TIME:845803,847305}What was that?{NOTE:うるさいじゃないの！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.26,0:14:14.97,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:851267,854979}If you hate each other so much, it's all over.{NOTE:こ、こんな憎しみあうなんて、もうおしまいだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.97,0:14:19.02,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:854979,859025}All of you loved volleyball… and it was\Nthe reason you joined the volleyball club.{NOTE:皆バレーが好きで、バレーを愛すればこそバレー部に入ったでしょ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.56,0:14:21.44,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:860568,861444}And yet…{NOTE:それなのに。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.77,0:14:24.07,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:862779,864072}And yet…!{NOTE:それなのに！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.40,0:14:27.32,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:866407,867325}Oh, Kozue.{NOTE:あ、こずえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.91,0:14:34.70,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:873915,874707}Kozue?{NOTE:こずえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.33,0:14:36.16,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:875333,876167}Oh, Midori.{NOTE:あ、みどり。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.04,0:14:38.87,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:877043,878878}I'm not surprised seeing you here.{NOTE:やっぱりここに来てたのね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.87,0:14:39.71,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:878878,879712}Yeah…{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.71,0:14:42.71,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:879712,882715}I always end up taking a walk here\Nwhenever I have breaks.{NOTE:休み時間になるとついこっち足が向っちゃうのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.71,0:14:43.88,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:882715,883883}Same here.{NOTE:私も。}
Comment: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:45.30,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:883883,885301}Hahaha.{NOTE:—ははは。\\N—ははは。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.88,0:14:50.26,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:886886,890264}That brawl yesterday was really intense.{NOTE:昨日のバレー部の大喧嘩凄かったわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.26,0:14:52.01,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:890264,892016}The whole school's talking about it.{NOTE:学校中その噂でも(XX・落ちきり)よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.72,0:14:53.43,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:892725,893434}Oh…{NOTE:あぁ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.43,0:14:54.97,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:893434,894977}Things are getting more and more messed up…{NOTE:ますます望みなしね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.85,0:14:56.97,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:895853,896979}Trouble, trouble!{NOTE:大変、大変！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.97,0:14:57.81,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:896979,897814}Trouble.{NOTE:大変。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.81,0:14:59.52,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:897814,899524}Serious trouble.{NOTE:一大事よ！ね、一大事。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.52,0:15:00.65,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:899524,900650}What is it, Naka?{NOTE:ナカどうしたのよ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.65,0:15:02.15,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:900650,902151}Wait… till you hear…{NOTE:うん…それがね…}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.15,0:15:04.57,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:902151,904570}Takeichi-san's group has gathered…{NOTE:今…武市さん達集まってさ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.57,0:15:07.28,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:904570,907281}…and are talking about how to reform the club.{NOTE:バレー部改革ののろしをあげたのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.28,0:15:08.03,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:907281,908032}Huh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.53,0:15:11.66,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:908533,911661}First of all, they decided that Captain Oonuma…{NOTE:先ずその手始めに、大沼さんにキャプテンの座だから…}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.66,0:15:13.83,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:911661,913830}…should give up her position of captain.{NOTE:XXXてもなくXXみんなで決めたの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.33,0:15:16.62,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:914330,916624}So they're reshuffling the team?{NOTE:このさいXXX真っ黒ってわけね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.62,0:15:17.45,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:916624,917458}Yeah.{NOTE:そうなのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.45,0:15:22.17,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:917458,922171}And that's why everyone says they'd like you two back in the club.{NOTE:だからさ…親分やみどり達にも…是非XX欲しいって皆が言ってんの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.17,0:15:23.08,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:922171,923089}Kozue.{NOTE:こずえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.08,0:15:24.50,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:923089,924507}What do we do?{NOTE:どうする？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.50,0:15:25.17,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:924507,925174}Hey.{NOTE:ね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.17,0:15:26.67,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:925174,926676}I refuse.{NOTE:私お断りするわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.80,0:15:29.42,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:927802,929429}Huh?! But why?{NOTE:え？どうしてよ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.42,0:15:34.43,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:929429,934434}It's a perfect opportunity to get back at Captain Oonuma for what she put us through.{NOTE:だって私達を散々苦しめてきた大沼キャプテンのワンマン体操をぶち壊す絶好のチャンスじゃないの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.39,0:15:36.64,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:935393,936644}I understand all that.{NOTE:分かってるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.64,0:15:38.06,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:936644,938062}But remember what I said yesterday?{NOTE:でも昨日も言ったんでしょう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.06,0:15:40.44,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:938062,940440}Deepening the conflict won't solve anything.{NOTE:これ以上は問題を対決しないって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.44,0:15:41.27,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:940440,941274}Besides…{NOTE:それに…}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.44,0:15:45.27,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:942442,945278}Even if Captain Oonuma forfeits her captain title now…{NOTE:今更大沼さんがキャプテンの座から降りたからって…}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.27,0:15:47.07,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:945278,947071}…nothing will really change.{NOTE:どうにもならないと思うの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.86,0:15:49.99,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:947864,949991}Nothing will truly change…{NOTE:もうどうにもならないのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.99,0:15:51.95,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:949991,951951}Principal's room{NOTE:校長室}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.20,0:15:53.78,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:952201,953786}What? Disband the volleyball club?{NOTE:え？バレー部を解散？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.74,0:15:56.08,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,{TIME:954745,956080}Precisely.{NOTE:そうです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.08,0:16:02.33,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,{TIME:956080,962336}I am very sorry to have to disband our volleyball club that has such a long winning tradition.{NOTE:伝統あるバレー部を解散するのは好調として私も大変残念に思うのですが…}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.33,0:16:05.21,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,{TIME:962336,965214}But it seems the club is undergoing a variety of problems.{NOTE:部内で色々問題を起こしているようだし。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.21,0:16:08.92,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,{TIME:965214,968926}I can't just continue to overlook its recent bad reputation.{NOTE:それにここまで悪い噂が広がっては放っとけませんな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.92,0:16:10.05,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:968926,970052}B-But…{NOTE:で、でも…}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.05,0:16:11.05,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,{TIME:970052,971053}No, no.{NOTE:いいえ、いいえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.05,0:16:15.01,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,{TIME:971053,975016}I understand your feelings\Nas the volleyball club's advisor very well.{NOTE:バレー部長としての清水先生のお気持ちはよく分かりますが…}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.01,0:16:17.81,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,{TIME:975016,977810}But if there is any budget for the volleyball club…{NOTE:だらけきった今のバレー部に回す予算があるなら…}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.81,0:16:23.23,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,{TIME:977810,983232}…the overwhelming opinion is that it is better to put it in more promising clubs.{NOTE:…もっと有望なクラブにつぎ込んだ方が良いという意見が圧倒的に多いんでね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.61,0:16:29.03,Default,Kanda,0,0,0,,{TIME:987612,989030}They've got some nerve.{NOTE:生意気だよね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.03,0:16:31.74,Default,Kanda,0,0,0,,{TIME:989030,991741}Making Captain Oonuma forfeit her title…{NOTE:大沼さんにキャプテン辞めろなんてさ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.74,0:16:33.28,Default,Suga,0,0,0,,{TIME:991741,993284}We can't let them off the hook.{NOTE:このまま放っとけないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.28,0:16:36.91,Default,Suga,0,0,0,,{TIME:993284,996913}We have to teach them a lesson, one that they won't forget.{NOTE:あんな生意気な新入りがこのさい決定的にとっちめましょうよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.70,0:16:41.54,Default,Nakahara,0,0,0,,{TIME:997705,1001542}But Takeichi-san and her friends are gathering evidence for the lime case…{NOTE:でも武市さん達石灰事件の証拠を集めて…}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.54,0:16:44.17,Default,Nakahara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1001542,1004170}…and if they do, we're done for.{NOTE:…それで私達解決しようとしてるのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.67,0:16:47.25,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1004670,1007256}I still don't understand why you did it.{NOTE:あなた達つまんないことしたものね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.25,0:16:49.13,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007256,1009133}Do you know how I feel now?{NOTE:人の気も知らないで。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.38,0:16:53.63,Default,Suga,0,0,0,,{TIME:1010384,1013638}But these first years trashed our club's traditions…{NOTE:だって一年生のくせにバレー部の伝統を…}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.63,0:16:56.18,Default,Kanda,0,0,0,,{TIME:1013638,1016182}Yeah. Besides, there's no evidence we did it.{NOTE:そうよ。それに証拠なんてどこにもないもん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.18,0:16:57.55,Default,Kanda,0,0,0,,{TIME:1016182,1017558}We don't have to worry.{NOTE:心配するほどないよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.55,0:16:59.26,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:1017558,1019268}– I guess you're right.\N– Okay.{NOTE:—本当よね。\\N—うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.26,0:17:00.97,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1019268,1020978}The evidence is right here.{NOTE:証拠ならここにあります。}
Comment: 0,0:17:00.97,0:17:02.23,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:1020978,1022230}– Ah?\N– Huh?!{NOTE:—あ？\\N—え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.23,0:17:03.52,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1022230,1023523}Professor Shimizu.{NOTE:清水先生。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.98,0:17:09.73,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1023981,1029737}I didn't want to add fuel to the fire,\Nso I hid Ayuhara-san's towel.{NOTE:これ以上バレー部内の騒ぎ大きくしたくないと思って……私鮎原さんのタオルを隠してしまったけど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.73,0:17:13.24,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1029737,1033241}Now I see that was a mistake.{NOTE:どうやら私のこうした思いやりが間違いだったと気がついたわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.65,0:17:17.91,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1034659,1037912}If you want to continue this farce no matter what…{NOTE:もしどうしてもあなた達が騒ぎ大きくするって言うなら…}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.91,0:17:20.70,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1037912,1040706}…I'm ready to call a witness who saw you.{NOTE:…石灰事件の証人を呼びましょうか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.70,0:17:21.41,Default,Nakahara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1040706,1041415}Eh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.41,0:17:22.62,Default,Nakahara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1041415,1042625}A witness?{NOTE:証人を？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.62,0:17:23.96,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1042625,1043960}Nakahara-san.{NOTE:中原さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.96,0:17:27.79,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1043960,1047797}A person from the track and field club saw you putting lime on that towel.{NOTE:あなたが石灰を持ち出しところ陸上部の人が見てるんですよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.79,0:17:30.80,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1047797,1050800}I asked her not to tell anyone about it…{NOTE:その人に私から頼んで黙ってもらってるけど…}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.80,0:17:33.17,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1050800,1053177}…but I can call her over here any time.{NOTE:…今ここに連れてきてもいいんですよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.55,0:17:37.64,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1056556,1057640}Oonuma-san.{NOTE:大沼さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.64,0:17:40.81,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1057640,1060810}Please gather everyone in the gym after school.{NOTE:放課後バレー部員全員体育館に集めてください。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.81,0:17:42.81,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1060810,1062812}I have something I'd like to talk about.{NOTE:お話ししたい事がありますから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.81,0:17:43.56,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1062812,1063563}I understand.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.56,0:17:47.90,Default,Nakahara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1066566,1067900}It's all over…{NOTE:もう駄目だわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.90,0:17:48.98,Default,Nakahara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1067900,1068985}What should I do?{NOTE:どうしよう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.98,0:17:51.86,Default,Nakahara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1068985,1071862}If it gets public, I'll get expelled…{NOTE:この事がバレたら私退学になるか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.78,0:17:55.99,Default,Nakahara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1072780,1075992}I… I'm dropping out of the volleyball club…{NOTE:もう私バレー部なんか辞めるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.36,0:17:59.62,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1078369,1079620}Girls.{NOTE:皆さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.62,0:18:04.00,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1079620,1084000}I want to apologize to everyone gathered here.{NOTE:今日ここに集まってもらったのは皆さんにお詫びがしたかったからです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.54,0:18:07.71,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1084542,1087712}Up until now, rather being the club's advisor…{NOTE:今までの私はバレー部長とのばかりで…}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.71,0:18:09.92,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1087712,1089922}…I was just a puppet for show.{NOTE:…ただ飾り人形にすぎませんでした。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.25,0:18:14.96,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1091257,1094969}The reason the volleyball club ended up like this…{NOTE:バレー部がこのようになったのも元はといえば私のこうした…}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.96,0:18:17.30,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1094969,1097305}…can be directly attributed to my indifference.{NOTE:…消極さが招いたものといえましょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.30,0:18:22.05,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1097305,1102059}I was uneasy about the club traditions\Nand so I left everything to Captain Oonuma.{NOTE:伝統の壁に負けて、大沼キャプテンに何もかも任せきりにしてきたことは…}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.05,0:18:25.27,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1102059,1105271}Now I am reflecting on that decision.{NOTE:…いけなかったことだと今私は猛烈に反省してるんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.89,0:18:27.98,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1106897,1107982}Professor!{NOTE:先生！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.98,0:18:31.81,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1107982,1111819}Do you mean I am disqualified as a captain?{NOTE:じゃ、キャプテンとしての私は失格だったとおっしゃるんですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.81,0:18:32.73,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1111819,1112737}Yes.{NOTE:え。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.73,0:18:34.57,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1112737,1114572}It was too much of a burden on you.{NOTE:やはり荷が重すぎたようですね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.57,0:18:38.45,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1114572,1118451}Not at all! I only wanted to protect the club traditions…!{NOTE:そんな！私は伝統守ってこれでも一生懸命に…}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.45,0:18:39.53,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1118451,1119535}Silence.{NOTE:お止めなさい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.53,0:18:40.49,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1119535,1120494}Huh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.95,0:18:44.83,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1120953,1124832}Under your captainship the club is at a point\Nwhere it can't be saved.{NOTE:もうバレー部あなた一人ではどうにも成らないところまで来てるんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.25,0:18:49.58,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1126250,1129587}The principal ordered\Nthe dissolution of the volleyball club.{NOTE:校長先生がバレー部の解散を命じになりました。}
Comment: 0,0:18:49.58,0:18:50.46,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:1129587,1130463}– Ah?\N– Huh?{NOTE:—あ？\\N—え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.00,0:18:53.25,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1132006,1133257}I can't believe it.{NOTE:そ、そんな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.25,0:18:54.84,Default,Ishikawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1133257,1134841}Professor, tell us it's not true!{NOTE:先生、嘘でしょう！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.34,0:18:57.97,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1136344,1137970}Unfortunately, it is.{NOTE:いいえ。本当です。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.97,0:19:00.89,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1137970,1140890}But I asked the principal.{NOTE:でも私は校長先生にお願いしました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.89,0:19:05.97,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1140890,1145978}I acknowledged I am responsible for this mess,\Nso I would like one last chance to clean it up.{NOTE:こうなったのも全て私の責任ですからもう一度立ち直るチャンスをいただきたいと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.35,0:19:11.65,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1147355,1151651}The principal agreed on one condition.{NOTE:そしたら校長先生は私達に一つの条件を出しになったんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.65,0:19:12.65,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1151651,1152652}One condition?{NOTE:条件。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.65,0:19:14.11,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1152652,1154111}Professor, what was it?{NOTE:先生、それは？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.11,0:19:18.11,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1154111,1158115}That is… to challenge Misawa Academy\Nto a match once again.{NOTE:それは…もう一度美沢学院に挑戦することです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.11,0:19:18.86,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1158115,1158866}Huh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.11,0:19:23.07,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1160117,1163079}If we win, we can keep the club running like always.{NOTE:そして勝てば今まで通りバレー部を続けさせるけど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.07,0:19:26.45,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1163079,1166457}But if we lose, it's disbanded immediately. That's the principal's condition.{NOTE:負ければ直ちに解散させると校長先生をおっしゃるんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.66,0:19:30.33,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1167667,1170336}So that just leave you girls, will you play the match?{NOTE:とにかくこの試合をやるかやらないか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.33,0:19:32.67,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1170336,1172672}Or will you let the club get disbanded?{NOTE:バレー部を解散するかしないか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.67,0:19:34.84,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1172672,1174840}Everything depends on you.{NOTE:これはあなた達部員全体の意見しだいです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.63,0:19:36.75,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1175633,1176759}Oonuma-san.{NOTE:大沼さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.75,0:19:39.05,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1176759,1179053}What is your opinion as the current captain?{NOTE:キャプテンとしてのあなたの意見はどうなんですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.01,0:19:42.59,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1180012,1182598}Now that Kanda-san's group are no longer regulars…{NOTE:神田さん達レギュラーが辞めてしまった以上。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.30,0:19:44.51,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1183307,1184517}I really…{NOTE:私としては…}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.51,0:19:46.39,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1184517,1186394}…can't play the match, correct?{NOTE:試合はできないって言うのね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.14,0:19:48.39,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1187144,1188396}Yes.{NOTE:え。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.39,0:19:50.64,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1188396,1190648}Therefore I quit the club.{NOTE:家のバレー部を辞めます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.64,0:19:51.39,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1190648,1191399}Very well.{NOTE:そう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.44,0:19:54.06,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1192441,1194068}Ayuhara-san, you?{NOTE:鮎原さん、あなたは？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.06,0:19:55.61,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1194068,1195611}Y-Yes…?{NOTE:は、はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.61,0:19:58.65,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1195611,1198656}Ayuhara-san, it's just like you wanted.{NOTE:鮎原さん。あなたの望み通り成ったわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.65,0:20:00.28,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1198656,1200282}The captain's title is free for you to take.{NOTE:キャプテンの座を譲るわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.28,0:20:01.90,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1200282,1201909}You must be so happy.{NOTE:嬉しいでしょう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.90,0:20:02.99,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1201909,1202993}Oonuma-san.{NOTE:大沼さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.99,0:20:06.49,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1202993,1206497}You can do whatever you want now.{NOTE:バレー部をどうしようとあなたの好きなようにしたらいいわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.49,0:20:10.71,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1206497,1210710}But I never said I wanted to be the captain.{NOTE:そんな。私何もキャプテンに成ろうなんて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.71,0:20:13.87,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1210710,1213879}Kozue, you don't owe her an explanation.{NOTE:こずえ。何も言い訳なんかすることないのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.87,0:20:16.59,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1213879,1216590}Oonuma-san tries to make it look like we've driven her out…{NOTE:大沼さん達はXXに酷いなこと言ってるけど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.59,0:20:21.55,Default,Hayakawa,1,1,0,,{TIME:1216590,1221554}But in reality, she doesn't think she can win the game\Nso she's shifting the responsibility to you.{NOTE:本当は美沢学院に勝てる自信がないものだから、その責任はあなたにXXせようとしてるのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.55,0:20:22.55,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1221554,1222555}Am I right?{NOTE:そうでしょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.55,0:20:23.93,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1222555,1223931}What a coward.{NOTE:卑怯なやり方ね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.93,0:20:25.05,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1223931,1225057}What…?{NOTE:何ですって？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.05,0:20:26.39,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1225057,1226392}Knock it off.{NOTE:お止しなさい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.39,0:20:27.76,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1226392,1227768}Enough with these fights!{NOTE:もうXXたくさんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.76,0:20:29.10,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1227768,1229103}I won't allow anything more.{NOTE:許しません。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.10,0:20:30.31,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1229103,1230312}E-Excuse me!{NOTE:失礼します。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.10,0:20:33.89,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1232106,1233899}Professor, I'm in.{NOTE:先生、私やります。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.89,0:20:34.60,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1233899,1234608}Me too.{NOTE:私も。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.60,0:20:35.77,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1234608,1235776}I'll do it too.{NOTE:私もやります。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.77,0:20:38.07,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:1235776,1238070}– Let us play as well.\N– Please.{NOTE:—私達もやらせてください。\\N—お願いします。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.65,0:20:43.32,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1239655,1243325}Alright then, we'll start practice tomorrow at 7 o'clock after school.{NOTE:じゃ、明日から放課後7時まで猛練習よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.32,0:20:45.70,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1243325,1245703}If you don't want to let the club get disbanded…{NOTE:バレー部を解散さしたくなかったら…}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.70,0:20:47.74,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1245703,1247747}…show up and give it your best.{NOTE:XXXも頑張ってちょうだい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.74,0:20:51.41,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1247747,1251417}I am going to become a proper coach, too.\NI won't go easy on you.{NOTE:私もこれから本当のバレーコーチとしてビシビシ至極から。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.41,0:20:53.33,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1251417,1253335}Be ready for it.{NOTE:皆十分覚悟しといてね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.33,0:20:54.08,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:1253335,1254086}– Yes ma'am!\N– Yes ma'am!{NOTE:—はい！\\N—はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.75,0:20:58.96,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1256756,1258966}Ayuhara-san, thank you.{NOTE:鮎原さん。有難う。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.34,0:20:59.96,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1259341,1259967}Huh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.55,0:21:04.55,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1260551,1264555}Seeing your enthusiasm for volleyball has finally given me motivation.{NOTE:あなたのバレーに対する情熱を見て私もやっと闘志が入ってきたのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.97,0:21:08.05,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1265973,1268058}Let's work hard, both of us.{NOTE:しっかりやりましょうね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.05,0:21:08.89,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1268058,1268893}Yes ma'am.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.31,0:21:14.44,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1273314,1274440}Hey, Kozue.{NOTE:ね、こずえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.44,0:21:16.56,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1274440,1276567}Let's forget about them already.{NOTE:嫌なことを早く忘れましょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.56,0:21:22.36,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1276567,1282364}If we lose with Misawa Academy because we dwelt too much on past, now that'll be trouble.{NOTE:こんなことにいつまでも拘ってもし美沢学院との試合に負けてもしたらそれほど大変よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.36,0:21:23.24,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1282364,1283240}Yeah.{NOTE:え。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.82,0:21:28.49,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1286827,1288496}Hey, watch it!{NOTE:おい、ぼやぼやするな！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.49,0:21:30.24,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1288496,1290247}Oh, it's you lovelies.{NOTE:何だ、お二人さんか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.24,0:21:31.70,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1290247,1291707}Tsutomu-kun?{NOTE:努くん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.70,0:21:33.41,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1291707,1293417}That was dangerous!{NOTE:酷いわ、いきなり。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.41,0:21:35.16,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1293417,1295169}Don't surprise me like that.{NOTE:ビックリさせないでよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.16,0:21:37.17,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1295169,1297171}Don't walk around all spaced out then.{NOTE:ぼんやり歩いてるからだよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.17,0:21:40.34,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1297171,1300341}Oh? Wait, both of you look pretty serious.{NOTE:おや？二人とも偉く深刻そうな顔してるじゃないか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.25,0:21:42.51,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1301258,1302510}I get it.{NOTE:そうか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.51,0:21:46.63,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1302510,1306639}Unlike middle school, there are a lot difficulties in high school…{NOTE:中学の時と違って、高校ともなれば色々と大変なんだな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.63,0:21:47.97,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1306639,1307973}Exactly.{NOTE:そうなのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.97,0:21:50.10,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1307973,1310100}I miss middle school.{NOTE:本当に中学の頃が懐かしいわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.10,0:21:54.60,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1310100,1314605}By the way, about that match with Misawa Academy that decides the survival of your club.{NOTE:ところで、バレー部の存続をかけて戦うという美沢学院との試合。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.60,0:21:57.19,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1314605,1317191}I'd say it'll be pretty difficult.{NOTE:そんな調子が勝つのはちょっと危ないな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.19,0:21:57.81,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1317191,1317817}Huh?!{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.85,0:22:00.86,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1318859,1320861}Hey, don't joke like that.{NOTE:ま、冗談言わないでよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.86,0:22:03.44,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1320861,1323447}We'll win for sure.\NRight, Kozue?{NOTE:絶対自身があるんだから。ね、こずえ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.44,0:22:04.07,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1323447,1324073}Yeah.{NOTE:え。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.07,0:22:07.70,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1324073,1327701}The club politics might be in bad shape,\Nbut we're fine on the court.{NOTE:部内のゴタゴタは嫌だけど、コートの中でなら大丈夫。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.70,0:22:09.20,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1327701,1329203}Are you sure about that?{NOTE:本当かな？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.20,0:22:11.45,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1329203,1331455}What is it supposed to mean, Tsutomu-san?{NOTE:ちょっと、努さん、失礼だわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.45,0:22:14.08,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1331455,1334083}Don't doubt our power.{NOTE:私の実力を打たないようなこと言わないでよ。}
Comment: 0,0:22:14.08,0:22:15.70,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1334083,1335709}Hahaha.{NOTE:ははは。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.70,0:22:19.63,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1335709,1339630}You're going to get burned if you get too confident looking at your past glory.{NOTE:過去の栄光におぶさっていい気になってるととんでもないことになるぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.63,0:22:22.46,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1339630,1342466}I want to show you something cool,\Nso come with me for a bit.{NOTE:君たちにいいものを見せてやるからちょっと僕についてこいよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.72,0:22:29.43,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1348722,1349431}We're here.{NOTE:ここだよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.55,0:22:31.30,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1350558,1351308}Here?{NOTE:ここは？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.39,0:22:32.85,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1351392,1352852}Mihara{NOTE:三原}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.14,0:22:37.10,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1353143,1357106}Yep. We're at Mihara Yumiko's house, the captain of Misawa Academy.{NOTE:そうだよ。美沢学院のキャプテン、三原ゆみこの家だよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.10,0:22:39.52,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1357106,1359525}How do you know where this is, Tsutomu-kun?{NOTE:努くんがどうしてここ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.52,0:22:41.44,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1359525,1361443}I deliver fruits here every day.{NOTE:毎日果物を届けるんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.44,0:22:42.73,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1361443,1362736}Let's go see the backside.{NOTE:さ、XX行こう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.49,0:22:50.36,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1369493,1370369}Check that out.{NOTE:あれを見れよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.29,0:22:58.25,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1375291,1378252}How do you like it? You've never seen anything like that, have you?{NOTE:どうだ？こんな練習見たことないだろう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.75,0:23:05.63,Alternative,Mihara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1383757,1385634}Famous attacker, Ayuhara-san.{NOTE:名アタッカーの鮎原さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.63,0:23:08.47,Alternative,Mihara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1385634,1388470}I'll counter your ball with these hands.{NOTE:きっとこの手であなたのボールを受けて見せるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.14,0:23:21.85,Default,Mihara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1400149,1401859}Alright, increase the speed!{NOTE:さ、もっとスピード上げて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.85,0:23:25.36,Default,Student,0,0,0,,{TIME:1401859,1405362}But if I raise it any further, the speed will be 80 km/h.{NOTE:でも、これ以上上げると時速は80キロになるわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.36,0:23:26.48,Default,Mihara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1405362,1406488}I don't care.{NOTE:構わないわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.53,0:23:31.86,Default,Student,0,0,0,,{TIME:1409533,1411869}You really are a superhuman, Captain.{NOTE:まったく超人的だわ、キャプテンは。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.24,0:23:33.53,Default,Student,0,0,0,,{TIME:1412244,1413537}Here goes.{NOTE:行くわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.53,0:23:34.20,Default,Mihara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1413537,1414204}Okay.{NOTE:オッケー。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.34,0:23:46.13,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1424340,1426133}Speed of 80 km/h…{NOTE:時速八十キロと言うと…}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.13,0:23:49.34,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1426133,1429345}It's twice as fast as a world's best girls' spike.{NOTE:女子最高のスパイクの倍以上の速さ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.34,0:23:50.93,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1429345,1430930}What a machine.{NOTE:恐ろしい刺激だわ。}
Comment: 0,0:23:57.43,0:23:57.43,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:1437436,1437436}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.98,0:24:03.02,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1439980,1443025}Fujimi High School team makes Kozue their new captain.{NOTE:こずえを新キャプテンにした富士見高校チームは…}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.02,0:24:07.40,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1443025,1447404}The match with Misawa Academy is drawing near.\NThe girls train restlessly every day.{NOTE:…美沢学園との試合を間近に控えて、特訓の日々を送るの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.40,0:24:10.19,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1447404,1450199}But somehow the team stays in low spirits.{NOTE:なぜか、チームを雰囲気が盛り上がらない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.19,0:24:14.91,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1450199,1454912}Kozue realizes that it is impossible for her\Nto replace the former captain.{NOTE:それがキャプテンの作るペースにやり自分では無理だと気付いたこずえは…}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.91,0:24:20.87,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1454912,1460876}She asks Oonuma Miyuki to come back to the club and complete the "machine gun attack" with her.{NOTE:…大沼みゆきにバレー部に戻りマシンガンアタックを完成してくれるよう頼みに言う。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.87,0:24:24.12,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1460876,1464129}Please look forward to the next episode.{NOTE:次回の「アタックナンバーワン」にご期待ください。}
